{"status":200,"title":"Success!","data":{"current_page":2,"data":[{"id":16,"uuid":"5b0f4e12-cd74-4c6d-abb5-e15a4843bbce","name":"Sid Mirza","email":"s.mirza@guild-realestate.com","thumbnail_image_path":"https:\/\/elist-solz.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com\/guild_real_estate\/upload\/listings\/thumbnail_400x520.jpg68f770c0b85ff.jpg","parent_id":32,"mobile":"+971525174031","team_id":null,"bio":"Originally from the United Kingdom, where he spent 31 years being raised and educated, Sid Mirza brings a wealth of international experience and a deep understanding of service, quality, and client satisfaction to Dubai\u2019s dynamic real estate market.\n\nWith a strong background in property management, Sid pays close attention to build quality, construction standards, and the upkeep of communal areas \u2014 ensuring his clients are presented only with properties that truly align with their lifestyle and expectations.\n\nHis extensive customer service experience in the UK has instilled in him the importance of listening, understanding, and delivering precisely what each client needs \u2014 not just during the sale, but also through thoughtful after-sales care that fosters long-term trust and comfort.\n\nHaving lived and worked in Dubai for the past three years, Sid has gained valuable insight into both the development side of the industry and how developers manage project delivery and broker relationships.\n\nAs an investor himself, Sid understands firsthand the process of buying and reselling property in Dubai \u2014 the challenges, the rewards, and the excitement of making the right investment decision. This personal experience enables him to guide clients with genuine understanding and practical expertise.\n\nSid\u2019s approach is personal, informed, and focused on ensuring every client finds a property that truly feels tailor-made for them.","image_path":"https:\/\/elist-solz.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com\/guild_real_estate\/upload\/listings\/400x520.jpg68f770c0b85ff.jpg","dis